      "author": "jqml",
      "description": "- Native property catalog for frontmatter property names and supported Obsidian-style property types.\n- Saved manual actions for adding, removing, renaming, and setting property values.\n- Create/move auto actions for Markdown notes entering configured target folders.\n- Preview, multi-file confirmation, and overwrite confirmation workflows.\n- Changed/skipped/failed result reporting with conflict reasons.\n- Supported property types: Text, List, Number, Checkbox, Date, Date & time, and Tags.\n",
